Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.47,0:23:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That time, forget-me-not
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.97,0:23:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not like love, not like loving, not something that's changing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only you I like, and that's how I think it will always be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.08,0:23:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Holding onto my aimless feelings, I look back as people often do
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.79,0:24:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stopping the scene were we chanced to meet from fading gently away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.31,0:24:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now if we can just find that thing.
